{"id":"rissah","term":"Rissah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Heap of ruins; dew, a station of the Israelites in the wilderness (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:21\">Num. 33:21</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:22\">22</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Numbers 33:21","Numbers 33:22"]}